        i0.ɵɵelementStart(184, "p", 12);
        i0.ɵɵtext(185, " Damien Leone is an American Writer, Director, Producer and Special Effects Artist. Damien is best known for writing and directing the Horror film \u201CAll Hallows' Eve\u201D in 2013 when he introduced to the world to his unrelenting killer, \u201CArt the Clown.\u201D He has gone on to thrill horror fans and receive critical acclaim with the release of the film \u201CTerrifier\u201D establishing \u201CArt the Clown\u201D as a legend in the horror genre. The upcoming sequel, \u201CTerrifier 2\u201D which will be released in 2022. Damien\u2019s incredible Special Effects will also appear in the upcoming horror film \u201CStream.\u201D Damien resides in New York City. ");
